Department of Citizenship and Immigration Act
SubjectCANADA - B.C. Immigration Agreement
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration enter into the CANADA-BRITISH COLUMBIA IMMIGRATION AGREEMENT to support mutual federal and provincial objectives in the areas of attraction, selection and settlement of immigrants and temporary residents wishing to reside in British Columbia.
